    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/5c5ec30e669cd9ee6d54708538df9848.poster.avif?t=1764729306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/5c5ec30e669cd9ee6d54708538df9848.webm?t=1764729306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/5c5ec30e669cd9ee6d54708538df9848.mp4?t=1764729306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《小贩人生》是一款兼具生活模拟和冒险元素的游戏，讲述了三个普通人尝试成为街头小贩的故事：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安德鲁斯：近期抵达美国的乌克兰移民</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梅兰妮：试图保住女儿监护权的离异母亲</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文尼：向来难以维持收支平衡的空想家</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/6f4ca86258a206b868b1d4efca2058e6.poster.avif?t=1764729306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/6f4ca86258a206b868b1d4efca2058e6.webm?t=1764729306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/6f4ca86258a206b868b1d4efca2058e6.mp4?t=1764729306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三位人物分别计划贩卖报纸、咖啡和面包圈，请引导他们度过各自的创业初始阶段。你能够以任意顺序体验他们相互交织的人生故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买贩卖车，并获取必要的许可证，然后开店营业。在储备货物之余，你还需要维护和升级贩卖车，从而赚取更多收入。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好预算管理，为物资供应、租金和个人需求合理分配资金。你能否赚取足够的资金谋生？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可自由探索城市，与当地人打成一片。但是千万不要迟到，否则你与顾客之间的关系会受到不良影响！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/ddcfb08c397e7ca03cb461756ec62b59.poster.avif?t=1764729306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/ddcfb08c397e7ca03cb461756ec62b59.webm?t=1764729306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324660/extras/ddcfb08c397e7ca03cb461756ec62b59.mp4?t=1764729306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>注意：《小贩人生》于2013年首次登陆Steam。虽然这款游戏赢得了三个独立游戏节奖项，并被《Polygon》和《Slant Magazine》等出版物评为有史以来最好的电子游戏之一，但该游戏始终未能彻底完成。其创作者Richard Hofmeier将与AdHoc Studio合作，于2023年发布该游戏的最终版本。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
